msgid "Two formats are accepted via ``--cap-source PATH``:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot.pcm:61
msgid ""
"``.nc`` -- a CEM ``baseline.nc`` written by ``run.py``. The ``install`` "
"data array (dims ``year x zone x tech``) is selected for the chosen year."
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot.pcm:64
msgid ""
"``.csv`` -- a tidy table with columns ``zone, tech, year, capacity`` "
"(MW). Useful when running PCM standalone, no CEM needed."
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot.pcm:67
msgid ""
"If neither is supplied, the existing fleet from ``tech_existing.csv`` is "
"used as-is (no expansion). This is the \"validate-the-existing-build\" "
"mode."
msgstr ""

